nodes.text: Star Wars: The Bad Batch, Volume 2 (Episodes 9-16)

Star Wars: The Bad Batch, Volume 2 (Episodes 9-16) is a forthcoming soundtrack featuring music composed by Kevin Kiner and his sons, Sean and Dean Kiner, for the latter eight episodes of the first season of Star Wars: The Bad Batch. It is scheduled to be released digitally on August 20, 2021.
